M|AI P|tx|tc framework for generating consistent, hi-qual im batches across AI md.
M|Prom|Buil|
M|Prom|tx|[Subject], [Setting], [Lighting]. [Style descriptor], [Composition]. [Mood adjectives]
M|Comp|- Su|Who/what is the focus. "A woman in a cream linen blazer"
M|Comp|- Se|Environment, background. "standing against a textured plaster wall"
M|Comp|- Li|Light qual and direction. "soft north-facing morning light"
M|Comp|- St|Genre, visual tradition. "editorial fashion photography"
M|Comp|- Co|Framing, camera angle. "md shot, rule of thirds"
M|Comp|- Mo|Emotional tone. "effortless, quiet confidence"
M|Midj|- `-|1, 16:9, 9:16)
M|Midj|it|`--style raw` for less AI interpretation
M|Midj|it|`--s 100-250` for less stylization (tighter to pm)
M|Midj|it|`--v 6` for latest md version
M|DALL|it|Include style keywords directly in the pm
M|DALL|it|Specify "photorealistic" for photo-like output
M|DALL|it|Use "no text, no watermark" in negative guidance
M|Krea|it|Use clear subject descriptions
M|Krea|it|Add camera/lens terms for photographic qual
M|Krea|it|Specify lighting conditions for mood control
M|Seed|it|Same seed produces similar composition
M|Seed|- Di|tests md variation range
M|Seed|it|Lock seed for variations of a single concept (change one cp, keep seed)
M|Seed|- Do|record seed, output qual, usable yes/no
M|Seed|**Se|**
M|Seed|tx|```
M|Seed|Batc|{id} \| md: {name} \| pm: {n}
M|Seed|tx|Seed -> qual -> Verdict
M|Seed|tx|1234567 -> Sharp, natural -> PASS
M|Seed|tx|2345678 -> Slight artifact on hand -> FAIL
M|Seed|tx|3456789 -> Background too busy -> FAIL
M|Seed|tx|```
M|Cons|1. *|Include the same style phrase in every pm ("editorial minimalism, natural lighting, clean backgrounds")
M|Cons|2. *|Specify exact colors ("warm cream tones, sage green accent, charcoal shadows")
M|Cons|3. *|When possible, use im prompting w/ a br-coherent reference
M|Cons|4. *|Lock the avoid list across all pm for a vt
M|Reje|Trac|
M|Reje|it|If specific hand poses fail repeatedly (>30% rejection rate), avoid hands in pm; crop or reframe
M|Reje|it|If complex backgrounds fail (>25%), simplify background description
M|Reje|it|If multiple subjects fail (>40%), gn single subject, composite later
M|Reje|it|If specific text in im fails (>60%), add text in post-production, not generation
M|Reje|tx|up the Style Spec based on rejection data. If a pattern exceeds 25% rejection rate, it shd be added to the Avoid list.
